articles.author: Tom Westbrook
articles.title: Asia stocks slip, dollar sell-off eases as dovish Fed cheer fades - Reuters
articles.description: Asian stocks backed away from 2-1/2-month highs on Wednesday and the dollar found support as investors' tempered some of their earlier enthusiasm about the prospect of an end to U.S. interest rate hikes.
